<item>
            <title>[LU-13947] ip2net syntax is broken</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13947</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following LUTF test cases are failing&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
lustre/tests/lutf/python/tests/suite_multi-rail/test_mr_UT_0025.py
lustre/tests/lutf/python/tests/suite_multi-rail/test_mr_UT_0030.py
lustre/tests/lutf/python/tests/suite_multi-rail/test_mr_UT_0040.py
lustre/tests/lutf/python/tests/suite_multi-rail/test_mr_UT_0045.py
lustre/tests/lutf/python/tests/suite_multi-rail/test_mr_UT_0050.py
lustre/tests/lutf/python/tests/suite_multi-rail/test_mr_UT_0095.py
lustre/tests/lutf/python/tests/suite_multi-rail/test_mr_UT_0096.py
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following ip2net syntax appears to no longer be accepted&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
tcp3(eth0[0,1]) 192.168.122.100
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Failure:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
1185 Sep  3 21:22:58 lustre01 kernel: LNetError: 10f-e: Error parsing &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;ip2nets=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;tcp3(eth0[0, 1]) 192.168.122.100&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
1186 Sep  3 21:22:58 lustre01 kernel: LNetError: 110-0: here.................................|--|
1187 Sep  3 21:22:58 lustre01 kernel: LNetError: 119-9: Error -22 parsing ip2nets
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
